                                    <div class="gap-10"></div>
                                    <p>Established in 1951 in Ahmedabad, India, the  Group has a legacy of over six decades in the Engineering and Construction Industry. A pioneer in this Industry, the Group’s customer centric and value based approach is the cornerstone of its success.</p>
                                    <p>The foundation of the  Group was laid by the visionary Shri Manibhai S. Patel, which has today grown to achieve an annual turnover of more than INR 7 Billion (USD 110 Million). His vision was backed by his brothers Mr. Hasmukhbhai S. Patel, a graduate in civil engineering and Mr. Manubhai S. Patel, a mechanical engineer. With exceptional entrepreneurial abilities coupled with technical expertise, the brothers spearheaded many crucial projects in infrastructure development nation-wide that firm-rooted the Group’s leadership in mammoth construction and engineering projects. </p>
